# Build for Raspberry Pi

CGO=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=arm go build

Enable raspberry pi i2c via raspi-config.
Connect Pin 3 (sda) to the green wire from the RJ10 cable from victron.
Connect Pin 5 (scl) to the red wire from the RJ10 cable from victron.

Start the application. It provides fuse status as prometheus export on :2117/metrics


